---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | ToolBox"
  description="Privacy policy for ToolBox – free online tools. Learn how we handle your data and use of Google AdSense."
  canonicalUrl="/privacy-policy"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: January 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          ToolBox ("we", "us", or "our") operates the website at yoursite.com. This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you use our service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Data We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          ToolBox tools run entirely in your browser. We do not collect, store, or transmit any data you enter into our tools. All calculations happen locally on your device.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
          We may collect basic analytics data (pages visited, approximate location by country, device type) through privacy-friendly analytics tools to understand how our site is used and improve it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Google AdSense & Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          This site uses Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google AdSense uses cookies to serve personalised ads based on your browsing history. You can opt out of personalised advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">
          Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on prior visits to this website and other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to users based on their visit to our site and other sites on the internet.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Cloudflare</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Our site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect IP addresses and request logs as part of its CDN and security services. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacy/" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a> for details.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          You have the right to request access to the personal data we hold about you, and to request its deletion. Since we do not collect personal data through our tools, there is generally nothing to access or delete beyond standard server logs.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via our <a href="/contact" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
